{"tid":2096752,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"大三罷兩青年涉襲便衣警 控方今加控暴動罪 7.21轉介區院答辯","createTime":"2020-07-06T10:30:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T11:13:52.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ff139629f285758cef41341fd42da842f84fb072","tid":2096752,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T10:30:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200706/ZUVFRY6WOKMQ66LIUQBYVCJIDQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200706%2FZUVFRY6WOKMQ66LIUQBYVCJIDQ%2F&d=HclisOHeH6vmzOJk9j96FvMFbVPULjdiAdi6tpyrPMY%3D&h=1cdc80e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200706%2FZUVFRY6WOKMQ66LIUQBYVCJIDQ%2F&h=fdcf955c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200706/ZUVFRY6WOKMQ66LIUQBYVCJIDQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n市民去年11月中一連五日進行三罷及堵路，其間有疑似便衣警在銅鑼灣金百利商場遭多人踢並及用雨傘打。事件中一名學生及一名酒吧侍應被捕，原本被控以襲擊致造成身體傷害罪，惟案件今在東區裁判法院再訊時，控方加控兩人暴動等罪，案件將於今年7月21日轉介區域法院答辯，其間兩人獲准繼續保釋。"},{"pid":"204259cc87c0258c89048f4b3ecbf1e52ab26dae","tid":2096752,"uid":362346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T10:30:27.000Z","msg":"fxxk"},{"pid":"31ccdd797b52a4750b90bfa3958453a242797cfe","tid":2096752,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"204259cc87c0258c89048f4b3ecbf1e52ab26dae","tid":2096752,"uid":362346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T10:30:27.000Z","msg":"fxxk"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T10:32:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f015cb5f7f6a804f153014a4eec19271c6d2f76","tid":2096752,"uid":201359,"like":0,"di